text: Óscar Nicanor Duarte Frutos (born 11 October 1956) is a Paraguayan politician. He served as President of Paraguay from 2003 to 2008. Nicanor Duarte announced his resignation as president, Nicanor renunciara mañana from Diario ABC Color. in order to assume a position as Senator on 1 July 2008. He presented his resignation on 23 June 2008 to the President of the Congress of Paraguay, Nicanor entrega hoy su renuncia al cargo from Diario ABC Color.
